### ===== AUTH SERVICE TESTS =====

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8081/auth/health

###

### 2. Inscription (Register)
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "test@bank.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phoneNumber": "0600000000"
}

###

### 3. Connexion (Login)
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@bank.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 4. Refresh Token (remplace TON_REFRESH_TOKEN par la valeur reçue au login)
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "TON_REFRESH_TOKEN"
}

###

### ===== CUSTOMER SERVICE TESTS =====

### 6. Health Check Customer
GET http://localhost:8082/customers/health

###

### 7. Créer un client
POST http://localhost:8082/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jean",
  "lastName": "Dupont",
  "email": "jean.dupont@email.com",
  "phoneNumber": "0700000001",
  "nationality": "Française",
  "address": "12 rue de la Paix",
  "city": "Paris",
  "country": "France"
}

###

### 8. Lister tous les clients
GET http://localhost:8082/customers

###

### 9. Obtenir un client par ID (remplace l'UUID)
GET http://localhost:8082/customers/CUSTOMER_ID_ICI

###

### 10. Vérifier un client (KYC)
POST http://localhost:8082/customers/CUSTOMER_ID_ICI/verify

###

### 11. Changer statut
PATCH http://localhost:8082/customers/CUSTOMER_ID_ICI/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

###

### ===== ACCOUNT SERVICE TESTS =====

### 12. Health Check Account
GET http://localhost:8083/accounts/health

###

### 13. Ouvrir un compte (remplace CUSTOMER_ID par un vrai UUID)
POST http://localhost:8083/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CUSTOMER_ID_ICI",
  "type": "COURANT",
  "currency": "XOF",
  "initialDeposit": 50000
}

###

### 14. Consulter les comptes d'un client
GET http://localhost:8083/accounts/customer/8db3dd00-15c1-49dc-9d20-d1c6377b6077

###

### 15. Créditer un compte
POST http://localhost:8083/accounts/ACCOUNT_ID_ICI/credit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 10000
}

###

### 16. Débiter un compte
POST http://localhost:8083/accounts/ACCOUNT_ID_ICI/debit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5000
}

###

### ===== API GATEWAY TESTS (quand gateway sera lancée) =====

### 5. Register via Gateway
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Gateway",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "gateway@bank.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ===== TRANSACTION SERVICE TESTS =====

### 17. Health Check Transaction
GET http://localhost:8084/transactions/health

###

### 18. Dépôt (remplace ACCOUNT_ID par un vrai UUID)
POST http://localhost:8084/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "DEPOT",
  "destinationAccountId": "ACCOUNT_ID_ICI",
  "amount": 50000,
  "currency": "XOF",
  "description": "Dépôt initial"
}

###

### 19. Retrait
POST http://localhost:8084/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "RETRAIT",
  "sourceAccountId": "ACCOUNT_ID_ICI",
  "amount": 10000,
  "currency": "XOF",
  "description": "Retrait guichet"
}

###

### 20. Transfert entre deux comptes
POST http://localhost:8084/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "TRANSFERT_INTRA",
  "sourceAccountId": "ACCOUNT_SOURCE_ID",
  "destinationAccountId": "ACCOUNT_DEST_ID",
  "amount": 5000,
  "currency": "XOF",
  "description": "Transfert client"
}

###

### 21. Historique d'un compte
GET http://localhost:8084/transactions/account/ACCOUNT_ID_ICI
